{
  "stem": "1473.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a thrill to take it out of the cupboard and wash them and, and use them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I got a new dress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I would get a new dress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and I remember always-- I think it's Shavuoth that we had the peonies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then my mother got peonies for the tiny apartment that we had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was very festive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Rosh Hashanah, they went to-- on Rosh Hashanah, my father wore a kittel, which is that white shroud that they wear.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And men were separated from women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we children used to play outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was always a small shul.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was a sad occasion because my mother mourned her parents very deeply-- very deeply.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, of course, it came out on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I imagine there must be because where my-- both my aunts lived in the 2nd District, it was very Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody sort of appeared to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But as for remembering beyond that, not much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember the neighborhood temple.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember the special shul for the High Holy Days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember the services.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everybody was Jewish, other than the children I went to school with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So at Christmastime, I remember being invited and being very impressed with a Christmas tree, and-- and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I also remember the talk of the anti-Semitism at home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my-- I think-- if I remember correctly, my mother spoke Yiddish-- Yiddish-German, German-Yiddish-- with her sisters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father spoke German, you know, the Viennese.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He could speak Yiddish, too, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at home-- my house, German was spoken, the Viennese-type German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I never did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Perhaps in adult circles, there was some.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
